  "reference_number": "RUS2288",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State has reasonable grounds to suspect BY INOVASYON TEKNOLOJI SANAYI VE TICARET LIMITED SIRKETI is an involved entity under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because it is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine by providing financial services, or making available funds, economic resources, goods or technology, that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n",
